dc_description_s: This data represents land use for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2020. [This dataset provides a comprehensive land use inventory for Dane County, Wisconsin. Parcel based land use inventory for Dane County Wisconsin for the year 2020, This dataset was developed for site specific and regional planning including land use, transportation and environmental resource applications. Parcel boundaries are reflective off April 1st 2020 while agricultural, specifically crop /field delineations and identifications are reflective of June-August 2020.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://gis-countyofdane.opendata.arcgis.com/.
